\partial_{x}u=\partial_{x}\xi\partial_{\xi}u + \partial_{x}\eta\partial_{\eta}u
\partial_{xx}u=\partial_{x}\left(\partial_{x}\xi\partial_{\xi}u + \partial_{x}\eta\partial_{\eta}u\right)\overset{?}{=}\partial_{xx}\xi\partial_{\xi}u + \partial_{x}\xi\partial_{x\xi}u + \partial_{xx}\eta\partial_{\eta}u + \partial_{x}\eta\partial_{x\eta}u
